Package org.cougaar.planning.plugin.asset

Interface Summary
AssetDataCallback Callback provided by AssetDataPlugin (or extension) to AssetDataReader implementation.
AssetDataReader Interface for classes that know how to read asset data from some media
 

Class Summary
AssetDataDBReader Populates an "Asset" from the config database.
AssetDataFileReader Parses local asset prototype-ini.dat to create local asset and the Report tasks associated with all the local asset's relationships.
AssetDataParamPlugin Extension of AssetDataPlugin which always uses the ParameterizedDataReader to construct the local entity asset and the Report tasks associated with all the local asset's relationships.
AssetDataParamReader Parses a set of parameters to create local asset.
AssetDataPlugin Generic plugin to create a local asset and the Report tasks associated with all the local asset's relationships.
AssetReportPlugin AssetReportPlugin manages REPORTFORDUTY and REPORTFORSERVICE relationships Handles both expansion and allocation of these tasks.
